Maisy AckleyHello, I'm Maisy Ackley. Feel free
to call me Maisy.

Maisy AckleyEven though I may not look like it,
I'm actually a third-year student. I'm here taking
care of injured students for the sake of
practicing healing magic.

Maisy AckleyIf you ever want to be healed, just
let me know anytime.

Maisy AckleyWould you like to receive healing
magic?

Phew... I finally made it back. It feels like I've
been underground for a really long time.

I heard that Hiyo-san found you, so I came flying
over.

I'm sorry... I got caught up in something
troublesome.
By the way, how were you treated while I was gone?

You were missing, you know. We were all searching
for you after school.

Only after school, huh... It seems like I'm not
that important after all.

Well, it's something that occasionally happens at
this school, you know.

Like being attacked by monsters, or getting
involved in forbidden research, or even high
jumping...

That's why the teacher doesn't search seriously
either. The police don't come from outside either.
But I'm glad you're safe too, Amelia.
You seem quite exhausted. Did something happen?
Just let me rest for now.
Ah, I hope Amelia gets better soon.
You must not go to the main hall right now.

I have to go to the underground magic research
club room now.

MasamuneShould we use the teleportation stone
we registered when we went there before? It was at
the entrance of B2, right?
Shall we start moving right away this time?

The suspicious place is still the Magic Research
Club room, right?

We got caught last time because of the detection
magic, but this time we know.

Bulletin Board: To prevent colds, let's
thoroughly wash our hands, gargle, or use
purification magic.

\c[10] I wonder if there's anyone who reads the
back of the bulletin board?
